From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Mike <michaelgorney4@gmail.com>
Date: Wed, 10 Jun 2026 20:40:08 -0400
Subject: [PATCH 52/58] Code clean-up

Goes through the net changes so far and cleans up a lot of bad code. Moved CXXMG declaration Sema ownership into SemaDeclCXXMG.cpp and removed duplicate bodies from SemaDeclCXX.cpp. Fixed conditional-member parser/AST lifetimes by replacing stored ArrayRef decl lists with owned decl storage plus arm index/count ranges. Added the non-CXXMG class-scope if parser guard. Split CXXMG expression factories into new ExprCXXMG.cpp. Added CXXMGImplementsExpr ASTImporter support. Implemented TreeTransform rebuild support for CXXMGTypeCheckExpr.

